data.description: MLS# 264197 Gorgeous 3 Bedroom 2 bath, Low Maintenance Stucco Townhome in the highly sought after neighborhood of Fountain Hills! Terrific Location that is close to everything! Inviting Exterior, Quality constructed Stucco Townhome with tile roof, Terrific Floor plan is light bright and open with vaulted ceilings. Large Living Room, Plenty of Cabinet and counter space with breakfast nook. Spacious Master Bedroom with ensuite a private patio and hot tub! Covered Patio, 2 car garage, a terrific value! This is an estate sale and home is being sold as is.
